en: Reset the counter and side job

zh_CN:
点击切换检测模型（当前：低精度）
暂不支持热切换（将重置已记录数据）
Tips：
影响识别准确率和速度，具体表现取决于CPU性能
此外选择尽量高的游戏分辨率也可以提高准确率
en:
Click to switch detection model (currently: low precision)
Hot switching is not supported yet (recorded data will be reset)
Tips:
Affects recognition accuracy and speed, the specific performance depends on CPU performance
In addition, choosing the highest possible game resolution can also improve accuracy
